{"tid":1757580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（同酬革命）【香港遊樂場協會—刻扣人工備忘錄】","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T15:28:15.000Z","uid":74965,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e29ab723c6e429a8f21f499d832b0d7137356d21","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"（轉載）<br />\n<br />\n1. 在13/11/2019，香港遊樂場協會仍然以19,830聘請社會工作助理(SWA)，<br />\n即刻扣了1,755(21,585-19,830)。<br />\n<br />\n2. 當我在26/11/2019將事實放出來的時候，香港遊樂場協會答左一大堆似是而非的回應。(圖二)<br />\n<br />\n3. 所以我翻閱〈香港遊樂場協會&mdash;業務檢討報告〉在《香港遊樂場協會2018-2019年報》發現在第13頁中提到(圖三)：<br />\n<br />\n2.7: 「截至31/03/2019，本會的儲備超過港幣五仟萬，比對去年大幅增長，也是歷史新高。」<br />\n<br />\n即是說，香港遊樂場協會即使儲備充足，仍然要壓低新入職同工薪酬。<br />\n<br />\n而香港遊樂場協會，係完全唔覺得有任何問題。<br />\n<br />\n就睇同工們，你地覺得有無問題。<br />\n<br />\n唔係淨係遊協既同工，係我地全部同工是否可忍受如此無良既機構。<br />\n<br />\n#同酬革命<br />\n<br />\n《香港遊樂場協會2018-2019年報》:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hq.hkpa.hk/upload/doc/HKPA_e-Annual_Report_18-19.pdf.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhq.hkpa.hk%2Fupload%2Fdoc%2FHKPA_e-Annual_Report_18-19.pdf.pdf&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx97hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=f08c5b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hq.hkpa.hk/upload/doc/HKPA_e-Annual_Report_18-19.pdf.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多社工上前線幫大家手，多年來因為林奠既一筆過撥款令好多前線社工被剝削，任人魚肉，但佢地仍然堅守本份，照顧弱勢社群，仲有好多社工出去食左好多tg，但而佢地就比ngo高層食哂佢地應得既野，大家幫手share同關注佢地<br />\n<br />\n兄分爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57e8f893949429d218a78407d7aa247beb3112b","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"1/10連"},{"pid":"37317cb6495c80306f0bf315c862c60cb1f76800","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"2/10連"},{"pid":"b7f3e280cbaae106196cf073fb188a9a989cc183","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"3/10連"},{"pid":"132389e73eb704237b1bb7d63c9debab06992943","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"4/10 連"},{"pid":"07a09b518d622a8aecfb74360b70f69dcd086d5f","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"5/10連"},{"pid":"15cce238fc0146c519a0426762eea964c736d947","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"6/10連"},{"pid":"ccb672367f0773c6adc7129a3037126d9b5069e8","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"7/10連"},{"pid":"b5fe3b0fd5e5852dcb89913e256148da456d8857","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"8/10連"},{"pid":"b83ea891688fb20b67af96a6f9d22c6f5cf5f043","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"9/10連"},{"pid":"5e76acd2d90eeec7a5f35fd7a315339b11999b23","tid":1757580,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"10/10連"},{"pid":"dcb33c4f7b080bea5781aeefcf5ca3236a09a136","tid":1757580,"uid":181767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"b35789d8269c140f6bbf9c7e0648f48c76419b55","tid":1757580,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"唔好開咁多線，先集中番五大訴求好嗎？<br />\n呢樣果樣，唔講以為已經贏左"},{"pid":"ee105bdca6eb8c1fef78e17dbcda85224181cf53","tid":1757580,"uid":86433,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:20:58.000Z","msg":"社工都唔係咩好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />篤灰狗 幫新移民 幾多時候係幫真香港人"},{"pid":"9c7c169bd2178a6301986b14a64f8756717b9cc6","tid":1757580,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0